: 208, \"to\": 221}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 234}, {\"ngram\": \"800m freestyle gold\", \"from\": 246, \"to\": 265}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 309, \"to\": 316}, {\"ngram\": \"a long-course World Championships\", \"from\": 320, \"to\": 353}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wiffen was only the sixth seed for Sunday's final but said he had swum within himself in winning his Saturday heat in 14:54.29.\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 483, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wiffen\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 362}, {\"ngram\": \"only the sixth seed\", \"from\": 367, \"to\": 386}, {\"ngram\": \"his Saturday heat\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He confirmed that by setting the pace from the off and led Turkey's Kuzey Tuncelli by four metres at the 500m mark.\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 600, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 544, \"end\": 550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9909456822442787, \"rank\": 0.008787328075424046, \"text\": \"Turkey\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pace\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 522}, {\"ngram\": \"four metres\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 582}, {\"ngram\": \"the 500m mark\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That gap was almost six seconds by halfway, as the 22-year-old was on course for world-record pace.\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 701, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That gap\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 610}, {\"ngram\": \"almost six seconds\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 633}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 678}, {\"ngram\": \"world-record pace\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 700}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At 1000m, Ukraine's Mykahilo Romanchuk was closest, over eight seconds behind, and it was clearly Wiffen against the clock.\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 826, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 713, \"end\": 720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9894774665543695, \"rank\": 0.010625137073739277, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"1000m\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 711}, {\"ngram\": \"Wiffen\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 807}, {\"ngram\": \"the clock\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Irish man's pace eased a little in the closing third but he still cruised to the gold medal in a new Irish record time of 14:34.07.\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 963, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 832, \"end\": 837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999532356025, \"rank\": 4.342680808235695e-08, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 933, \"end\": 938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999532356025, \"rank\": 4.342680808235695e-08, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the closing third\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 884}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 923}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Germany's Florian Wellbrock finished second in 14:44.61 with Frenchman David Aubry third in 14:44.85.\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 1066, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 965, \"end\": 972, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9168375212701906, \"rank\": 0.0905472736774785, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1036, \"end\": 1047, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Aubry\", \"score\": 0.9998308064058119, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Aubry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Aubry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Aubry\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That race was definitely better for me,\\\" Wiffen said afterwards.\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1133, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That race\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1078}, {\"ngram\": \"Wiffen\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1116}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Coming here, the progression from the 400 to the 800 to the 1500, I am so happy to come away with a PB and two world titles.\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1259, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1235, \"end\": 1237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Byte\", \"score\": 0.9999972251118681, \"rank\": 2.740762771159209e-06, \"text\": \"PB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Byte\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Byte\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two world titles\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1258}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am so happy because after hitting that time in April, it could have been a fluke.\", \"from\": 1261, \"to\": 1345, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that time\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1307}, {\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1316}, {\"ngram\": \"a fluke\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1344}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I went 14:35 in the U23s, in my back garden really, in Dublin.\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1401, \"end\": 1407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_GAA\", \"score\": 0.9996290845803286, \"rank\": 0.00037105276013712823, \"text\": \"Dublin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_GAA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_GAA\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the U23s\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1370}, {\"ngram\": \"my back garden\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1389}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was talking about it with my coach Andi [Manley] - and we had a little bet as to whether I was going to PB or not - but [the plan was] 100% to go out a bit faster than everybody else and just be in my own lane, get out ahead and really focus on what I was going to do.\\\"\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1682, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my coach\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1447}, {\"ngram\": \"Andi [Manley\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1460}, {\"ngram\": \"a little bet\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1487}, {\"ngram\": \"PB\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1519}, {\"ngram\": \"the plan\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1542}, {\"ngram\": \"100%\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1552}, {\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1590}, {\"ngram\": \"my own lane\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1622}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wiffen was two and a half seconds outside the championship record and six off the world-record mark set by Sun Yang at the 2012 Olympics, which he has firmly in his sights.\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1856, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1791, \"end\": 1799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Yang\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sun Yang\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Yang\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Yang\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wiffen\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1690}, {\"ngram\": \"the championship record\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1749}, {\"ngram\": \"the world-record mark\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1783}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2012 Olympics\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1820}, {\"ngram\": \"his sights\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1855}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's definitely one of my goals to try and beat that at some point,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1936, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my goals\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1890}, {\"ngram\": \"some point\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 1925}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am only 22, I have got at least another eight years, another couple of Olympics in me.\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 2027, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"at least another eight years\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 1992}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2020}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am sure it'll go at some stage and I hope to be the person to do it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2099, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some stage\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2060}, {\"ngram\": \"the person\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2088}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mona McSharryfinished eighth in the 50m breaststroke final, her third of the championships.\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2101, \"end\": 2105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_Vanderwaal\", \"score\": 0.9999987728668456, \"rank\": 1.2271340624978171e-06, \"text\": \"Mona\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_Vanderwaal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_Vanderwaal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 50m breaststroke\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2153}, {\"ngram\": \"the championships\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2191}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Sligo woman had come into the race with the joint sixth-fastest qualifying time but a long week seemed to show as she tired in the closing metres to finish in a time of 30.96 seconds, 0.33 slower than her semi-final performance yesterday.\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2436, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2198, \"end\": 2203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\",