e to move through a long meet, perform well and move through the rounds is definitely something positive.\\\"\", \"from\": 2798, \"to\": 2914, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a long meet\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2837}, {\"ngram\": \"the rounds\", \"from\": 2869, \"to\": 2879}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2894, \"to\": 2903}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier on Sunday, Ireland's 4x100m men's medley relay team made a piece of swimming history as they reached the final while the women's relay team's place at the 2024 Olympic Games was confirmed.\", \"from\": 2916, \"to\": 3112, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2935, \"end\": 2942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.999997802058402, \"rank\": 2.1978348389467447e-06, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 2927, \"to\": 2933}, {\"ngram\": \"a piece\", \"from\": 2981, \"to\": 2988}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming history\", \"from\": 2992, \"to\": 3008}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's relay team's place\", \"from\": 3041, \"to\": 3071}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 3075, \"to\": 3097}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Conor Ferguson [backstroke], Darragh Green [breaststroke], Max McCusker [butterfly] and Shane Ryan [freestyle] confirmed their spot in the final after an outstanding swim of 3:34.94 to place fourth in their heat and eighth overall.\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3345, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Conor Ferguson\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3128}, {\"ngram\": \"Darragh Green\", \"from\": 3143, \"to\": 3156}, {\"ngram\": \"Shane Ryan\", \"from\": 3202, \"to\": 3212}, {\"ngram\": \"their spot\", \"from\": 3235, \"to\": 3245}, {\"ngram\": \"an outstanding swim\", \"from\": 3265, \"to\": 3284}, {\"ngram\": \"3:34.94\", \"from\": 3288, \"to\": 3295}, {\"ngr